Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:19.02,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}知らない言葉を　覚えてゆくたび
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:25.52,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}おもかげのなか　手を伸ばすの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:32.12,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}だけど一人では　分からない言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:35.63,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あるのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:40.22,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}さよならは　苦くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:47.28,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}アイシテルは　遠いにおいがした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:55.37,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}例えようのない　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:02:02.69,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}とても怖くて　だけど　とても愛おしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:08.95,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}わたし　なんで　泣いてるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:15.68,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}心になんて　答えたらいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:22.43,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}言葉はいつでも　語るでもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:28.67,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}そこにあるばかり　つのるばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:37.51,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}わたしは　あなたに　会いたくなる
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:19.02,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}每當記憶陌生詞彙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:25.52,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}雙手便不由自主   伸向舊日光景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:32.12,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}但孤身一人    也許有些話語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:35.63,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}難以領悟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:40.22,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一句「再見」傷感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:47.28,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一聲「愛你」遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:55.37,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}這份思念無法言喻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:02:02.69,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}讓人惶恐    卻又無比令人憐惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:08.95,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}我眼中的淚 到底為何而流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:15.68,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}糾纏不清的心 到底如何回應
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:22.43,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}總會口不對心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:28.67,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}埋藏在心裡    一句又一句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:37.51,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}我止不住地想見到你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:21.27,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あなたの声がみちしるべ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:42.73,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}一羽の鳥が　鳴いている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:53.79,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}名前のない空に　わたしを探して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:59.61,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}優しさで編み続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:05.25,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}ゆりかごで明日へ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:11.28,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}晴れの日も雨の日にも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:15.97,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あなたを守るために
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:26.88,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}かけがえのない宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:37.70,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}名前のない花は　静かに眠るよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:21.27,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}你的聲音 指引我向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:42.73,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一隻小鳥 婉轉鳴叫著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:53.79,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在未知的天空中 四處尋找我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:59.61,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在溫柔編織出的搖籃裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:05.25,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}向著明天前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:11.28,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}不論天晴 不論風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:15.97,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}只為能守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:26.88,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}獨一無二的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:37.70,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}無名之花 靜靜地沉眠
